Description: 
v4l2codecs: Update videodev2.h with NV12MT_COL128 and
 NV12MT_10_COL128

These formats are being upstreamed at present for the Raspberry Pi
HEVC decoder. Add them so that we can get Fluster running and validate
the driver.
 .
 gst-plugins-bad1.0 (1.26.2-3) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * d/patches: 0001-h266parser-Fix-overflow-when-parsing-subpic_level_in.patch
     - Fix CVE-2025-6663 (Closes: #1108973)
       Fix overflow when parsing subpic_level_info in H.266 parser
Author: Marc Leeman <marc.leeman@gmail.com>
Bug-Debian: https://bugs.debian.org/1108973

---
